  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>OVERVIEW</strong></h2>Drive through the busy streets of Dabbo City on iconic Filipino jeepneys. Pick up passengers, return their change, and drop them off at their destination. Use your hard-earned income to feed your family, buy furniture, and pay your rent. Or spend it on upgrades and customization options for your jeeps.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>IMMERSIVE GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489990/extras/d104849dbb0c0e4bfe68e6a3f5cd0096.poster.avif?t=1694866586\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489990/extras/d104849dbb0c0e4bfe68e6a3f5cd0096.webm?t=1694866586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489990/extras/d104849dbb0c0e4bfe68e6a3f5cd0096.mp4?t=1694866586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Take a walk to the garage, push the engine button, and switch your gear! Become the jeepney driver!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CUSTOMIZATION</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489990/extras/907eda2913c9261f5a667b0fe4ca1091.poster.avif?t=1694866586\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489990/extras/907eda2913c9261f5a667b0fe4ca1091.webm?t=1694866586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489990/extras/907eda2913c9261f5a667b0fe4ca1091.mp4?t=1694866586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Upgrade your jeepney's speed, fuel efficiency, and fuel capacity. Paint it to one of many colors. Golden jeepney, anyone?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>REALISTIC TRAFFIC SYSTEM</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489990/extras/eba2e6f00e29ce15d4f585bb5be780dc.poster.avif?t=1694866586\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489990/extras/eba2e6f00e29ce15d4f585bb5be780dc.webm?t=1694866586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489990/extras/eba2e6f00e29ce15d4f585bb5be780dc.mp4?t=1694866586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Navigate the busy streets and weave through traffic!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FAMILY MANAGEMENT</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489990/extras/b9e162871fea9913bf663c65571de69c.poster.avif?t=1694866586\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489990/extras/b9e162871fea9913bf663c65571de69c.webm?t=1694866586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489990/extras/b9e162871fea9913bf663c65571de69c.mp4?t=1694866586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Manage your family's health and happiness by interacting with them, buying furniture, and picking the right choices in randomized events!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HIRAYA CORPORATION</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489990/extras/d099f4128923276d3fe2743883419d8c.poster.avif?t=1694866586\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489990/extras/d099f4128923276d3fe2743883419d8c.webm?t=1694866586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489990/extras/d099f4128923276d3fe2743883419d8c.mp4?t=1694866586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Discover the secrets of a megacorporation as it slowly starts to take over the country...",
